flowchart TD
    Start([Staff Member]) --> CheckSession{Session<br/>Exists?}

    CheckSession -->|Yes| AutoLogin[Automatically<br/>Load Dashboard]
    CheckSession -->|No| ShowLogin[Show Login Screen]

    ShowLogin --> EnterPassword[Enter Access Password]
    EnterPassword --> ValidatePassword{Password<br/>Valid?}

    ValidatePassword -->|No| CheckAttempts{Attempts<br/>> 5?}
    CheckAttempts -->|No| ShowError[Show Error:<br/>'Invalid Password']
    ShowError --> EnterPassword

    CheckAttempts -->|Yes| RateLimited[Account Locked<br/>15 Minutes]
    RateLimited --> WaitCooldown[Wait for<br/>Cooldown Period]
    WaitCooldown --> ShowLogin

    ValidatePassword -->|Yes| SaveSession[Save Session<br/>in Browser]
    SaveSession --> LoadDashboard[Load Voicemail<br/>Dashboard]

    AutoLogin --> LoadDashboard

    LoadDashboard --> DashboardReady[Dashboard Ready]
    DashboardReady --> AutoRefresh[Auto-Refresh<br/>Every 30 Seconds]

    DashboardReady --> UserActions{User Action}
    UserActions -->|Logout| ClearSession[Clear Session]
    ClearSession --> ShowLogin

    UserActions -->|Continue Working| DashboardReady

